item.title: About
item.author: arcytech77@gmail.com (Andrew Ryan Carpenter)
item.description: The Author I’m a fullstack engineer, living in San Francisco. I’ve been working in the bay area for the past four years with a focus on building clean UI’s for the end user. I recieved my bachelors degree in Physics at the University of Hawaii in 2013 and continued to do research on the mini Time Cube (mTC) experiment before switching to software.
